cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL 

The paper deals with computer vision and robotics, specifically the detection of curbs using LIDAR data. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves real-time processing and tracking, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The use of deep networks for processing the data suggests that the paper may also belong to the categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper involves natural language processing for describing the approach, which could potentially place it in the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL).
